import react from 'react';
import { Col, Row, Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input } from 'reactstrap';
  
const Article = (props) => {
    return (
        /*Produto*/
        <Form>
            <Row form>
            <Col md={6}>
                <FormGroup>
                <Label for="CodigoProduto">C贸digo: </Label>
                <Input type="codigo" name="codigo" id="Formcodigo" placeholder="inserir c贸digo" />
                </FormGroup>
            </Col>
            </Row>

            <Row form>
            <Col md={6}>
                <FormGroup>
                <Label for="CodigoProduto">Nome: </Label>
                <Input type="codigo" name="codigo" id="Formcodigo" placeholder="inserir c贸digo" />
                </FormGroup>
            </Col>
            </Row>

            <Row form>
            <Col md={6}>
                <FormGroup>
                <Label for="CodigoProduto">Quantidade:</Label>
                <Input type="codigo" name="codigo" id="Formcodigo" placeholder="inserir c贸digo" />
                </FormGroup>
            </Col>
            </Row>
        
        <FormGroup check>
          <Input type="checkbox" name="check" id="exampleCheck"/>
          <Label for="exampleCheck" check>Check me out</Label>
        </FormGroup>
        <Button>Salvar</Button>
      </Form>
    );
  }
  
           
      


export default Article;
